---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="ELRS Mobile - Control Your Hardware">
	<main>
		<header>
			<h1>ELRS <span class="text-gradient">Mobile</span></h1>
			<p class="tagline">Supports ELRS Versions 3.x.x and 4.x.x</p>
			<div class="cta-group">
				<a href="https://github.com/wbhinton/ELRS-Mobile/releases" class="button primary">Download APK</a>
				<a href="/user_guide" class="button secondary">Documentation</a>
				<a href="https://github.com/wbhinton/ELRS-Mobile" class="button secondary">GitHub</a>
			</div>
		</header>

		<section id="overview">
			<h2>Overview</h2>
			<p>
				ELRS Mobile is an comprehensive open-source solution for flashing and configureing ExpressLRS hardware. 
				Providing cached firmware for completely offline operation and a convenient interface for the ELRS WebUI for device configuration.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section id="demo">
			<h2>See it in Action</h2>
			<div class="video-container">
				<div class="phone-mockup">
					<iframe 
						width="100%" 
						height="100%" 
						src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6tukOoXa5aQ?autoplay=0&loop=1&rel=0&controls=1" 
						title="ELRS Mobile Demo" 
						frameborder="0" 
						allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" 
						allowfullscreen>
					</iframe>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="app-stores">
			<h2>Official App Stores</h2>
			<p>We are working hard to bring ELRS Mobile to your favorite app stores. Approval and publishing is currently in progress.</p>
			<div class="store-grid">
				<div class="store-card disabled">
					<div class="store-icon">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M17.523 15.3414L20.355 13.706C21.215 13.209 21.215 11.961 20.355 11.464L17.523 9.82944L14.771 12.5834L17.523 15.3414ZM13.883 13.4724L16.635 16.2234L5.656 22.564C5.071 22.902 4.331 22.795 3.865 22.28L13.883 13.4724ZM3.535 20.916L12.997 12.5844L3.535 4.25144C3.195 4.41444 3 4.76744 3 5.16644V20.0014C3 20.4 3.195 20.7534 3.535 20.916ZM13.883 11.6964L3.865 2.88844C4.331 2.37344 5.071 2.26644 5.656 2.60444L16.635 8.94544L13.883 11.6964Z"/></svg>
					</div>
					<div class="store-info">
						<h3>Google Play</h3>
						<span class="status">In Review</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="store-card disabled">
					<div class="store-icon">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M17.05 20.28c-.96.95-2.06 1.92-3.4 1.92s-1.8-.84-3.37-.84-2.1.84-3.41.84c-1.28 0-2.43-1.02-3.41-2.45C1.45 16.71.36 12.44 2.45 9.15c1-1.5 2.51-2.48 4.14-2.48 1.4 0 2.4 1.05 3.4 1.05s2.2-.9 3.55-.9c1.1 0 2.45.6 3.45 1.7-2.7 1.6-2.2 5.3 0 6.6-.7 1.8-1.7 3.6-2.94 5.16zM13 2c0 1.5-1.26 3.1-2.9 3.1-.15-1.9 1.4-3.5 2.9-3.5z"/></svg>
					</div>
					<div class="store-info">
						<h3>App Store</h3>
						<span class="status">Coming Soon</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="hardware">
			<h2>Supported Hardware</h2>
			<p>ELRS Mobile supports a wide range of ExpressLRS targets, focusing on Wi-Fi capable hardware.</p>
			<div class="hardware-grid">
				<div class="hw-card">
					<h4>Platforms</h4>
					<ul>
						<li>ESP8285</li>
						<li>ESP32</li>
						<li>ESP32-C3</li>
						<li>ESP32-S3</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="hw-card">
					<h4>Tested Targets</h4>
					<ul>
						<li>RadioMaster XR1 / XR4 Dual Band</li>
						<li>BETAFPV SuperP 14Ch (2.4G & 900M)</li>
						<li>HappyModel EP / EP Dual</li>
						<li>RadioMaster Nomad / Pocket</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
			<p class="note">Currently unsupported: STM32 targets requiring serial STLink or Betaflight Passthrough.</p>
		</section>

		<section id="features" class="grid">
			<div class="card">
				<h3>Device Discovery</h3>
				<p>Seamlessly locate ELRS devices via mDNS, static AP IP (10.0.0.1), or manual override for complex networks.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card">
				<h3>Smart Flashing</h3>
				<p>The system patches firmware with your unique credentials (SSID, Binding Phrase) automatically before flashing OTA.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card">
				<h3>Connection Resilience</h3>
				<p>A multi-stage heartbeat monitor ensures you stay connected during transient network drops with a smart 30-second grace period.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card">
				<h3>Expert Mode</h3>
				<p>Enable advanced auditing by saving assembled binaries locally for inspection or manual flashing via STLink/FTDI.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="installation">
			<h2>Installation</h2>
			<div class="install-steps">
				<div class="step">
					<span class="step-number">1</span>
					<p>Go to <a href="https://github.com/wbhinton/ELRS-Mobile/releases">Releases</a> and download the latest <code>.apk</code>.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="step">
					<span class="step-number">2</span>
					<p>Enable <strong>Install from Unknown Sources</strong> in your Android settings.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="step">
					<span class="step-number">3</span>
					<p>Open the APK and follow the installation prompts.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<footer>
			<p>&copy; 2026 Weston Hinton. Distributed under the GNU GPL v3.</p>
		</footer>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	header {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 4rem 0;
	}
	h1 {
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		margin: 0;
	}
	.text-gradient {
		background-image: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--primary), #ffffff);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-size: 400%;
		background-position: 0%;
	}
	.tagline {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}
	.cta-group {
		margin-top: 2rem;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 1rem;
	}
	.button {
		padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: bold;
		transition: transform 0.2s, background 0.2s;
	}
	.button:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}
	.button.primary {
		background: var(--primary);
		color: white;
	}
	.button.secondary {
		border: 1px solid var(--primary);
		color: var(--primary);
	}
	section {
		padding: 3rem 0;
	}
	h2 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		border-bottom: 2px solid var(--surface);
		padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}
	.video-container {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		padding: 2rem 0;
	}
	.phone-mockup {
		position: relative;
		width: 300px;
		height: 600px;
		background: #000;
		border: 12px solid #2d2d2d;
		border-radius: 36px;
		overflow: hidden;
		box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
	}
	.phone-mockup::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		width: 150px;
		height: 25px;
		background: #2d2d2d;
		border-bottom-left-radius: 12px;
		border-bottom-right-radius: 12px;
		z-index: 10;
	}
	.store-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}
	.store-card {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background: var(--surface);
		border-radius: 16px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(0, 191, 165, 0.2);
		gap: 1.2rem;
		transition: transform 0.2s ease;
	}
	.store-card.disabled {
		opacity: 0.8;
		filter: grayscale(0.5);
	}
	.store-icon svg {
		width: 40px;
		height: 40px;
		color: var(--primary);
	}
	.store-info h3 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
	}
	.store-info .status {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: var(--primary);
		opacity: 0.8;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	}
	.hardware-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 2rem;
		margin: 2rem 0;
	}
	.hw-card {
		background: var(--surface);
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
	}
	.hw-card h4 {
		margin-top: 0;
		color: var(--primary);
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--background);
		padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}
	.hw-card ul {
		margin: 0;
		padding-left: 1.2rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}
	.note {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-style: italic;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		text-align: center;
	}
	.grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}
	.card {
		background: var(--surface);
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 1px solid transparent;
		transition: border-color 0.2s;
	}
	.card:hover {
		border-color: var(--primary);
	}
	.card h3 {
		margin-top: 0;
		color: var(--primary);
	}
	.install-steps {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}
	.step {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		background: var(--surface);
		padding: 1rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
	}
	.step-number {
		background: var(--primary);
		color: white;
		width: 32px;
		height: 32px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		border-radius: 50%;
		font-weight: bold;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}
	footer {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 2rem 0;
		margin-top: 4rem;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--surface);
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}
	a {
		color: var(--primary);
		text-decoration: none;
	}
	a:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}
</style>
